      <heading>
        Software documentation for the TTIOAccessUnit class
      </heading>
      <class name="TTIOAccessUnit" super="NSObject">
        <declared>TTIOAccessUnit.h</declared>
        <desc>
          Transport-layer Access Unit: one spectrum as
          a transport payload. ``spectrumClass`` wire values: 0 =
          MassSpectrum, 1 = NMRSpectrum, 2 = NMR2D, 3 =
          FID, 4 = MSImagePixel, 5 = GenomicRead ``polarity`` wire
          values (differs from TTIOPolarity which uses -1 for
          negative; the wire uses nonneg only): 0 = positive,
          1 = negative, 2 = unknown
        </desc>
        <method type="instancetype" factory="yes">
          <sel>decodeFromBytes:</sel>
          <arg type="const uint8_t*">bytes</arg>
          <sel>length:</sel>
          <arg type="NSUInteger">length</arg>
